					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8106275#post-4036362</guid>
				<title>A Nice SCP</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8106275/scp-4443#post-4036362</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 24 Oct 2018 18:16:17 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lady Zero</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3893891</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is a good SCP, it's clever, it's halloween-related, it's even got an element of whimsy to it. There's nothing groundbreaking about it, and it could greatly benefit from a picture of the object (though as a visual person, I may be biased), but as far as I know it's an original idea, and it works well enough into Halloween.</p> <p>+1 for concept and decent execution, hope to see where this goes.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
